article_title: Ted Cruz wins Wyoming’s 14 GOP delegates
article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

Thunderstorms. High 56F. Winds NNE at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 90%..

Tonight

Thunderstorms early, mainly cloudy overnight with a few showers. Low 42F. Winds N at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 80%.

article_metadata.author: Laura Hancock, Casper Star-Tribune

og.description: CASPER – GOP presidential hopeful Ted Cruz said Saturday his policies will restore coal jobs in Wyoming and help Western states claim public lands – words that resonated with Wyoming
